msgstr "Aktivira neke pomodne animacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Groups"
msgstr "Grupe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can group downloads."
msgstr "Preuzimanja možete grupisati."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Groups</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Grupe u <application>KGetu</application>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Groups</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Grupe u <application>KGetu</application>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use default folders for groups as suggestion"
msgstr "Podrazumevane fascikle za grupe kao predlozi"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tick this box if you want &kget; to use default folders for your downloads."
msgstr ""
"Popunite ovu kućicu ako želite da <application>KGet</application> preuzima u "
"podrazumevane fascikle."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network"
msgstr "Mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can modify your network related settings here."
msgstr "Ovde možete izmeniti postavke u vezi sa mrežom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Network</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mreža u <application>KGetu</application>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Network</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mreža u <application>KGetu</application>.</phrase>"

# >! ui: Limit Maximum Downloads Per Group -> Limit Maximum Downloads Per Group
#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit Maximum Downloads Per Group"
msgstr "Najviše preuzimanja po grupi:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want Download limits to be implemented."
msgstr "Popunite ovu kućicu da bi se primenjivala ograničenja preuzimanja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed Limit"
msgstr "Ograničenje brzine"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want the Global speed limits to be used."
msgstr "Popunite ovu kućicu da bi se primenjivalo globalna ograničenja brzine."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global download limit"
msgstr "Globalno ograničenje preuzimanja:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum global download limit."
msgstr "Postavite globalno gornje ograničenje za preuzimanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global upload limit"
msgstr "Globalno ograničenje otpremanja:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum upload limit."
msgstr "Postavite globalno gornje ograničenje za otpremanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconnect on Broken Connection"
msgstr "Ponovno povezivanje pri prekidu veze"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want &kget; to reconnect after an error or a broken "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Popunite ovu kućicu da bi se <application>KGet</application> ponovo povezao "
"posle greške ili prekida veze."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of retries"
msgstr "Broj pokušaja:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum number of time &kget; will try to reconnect."
msgstr ""
"Postavite koliko će najviše puta <application>KGet</application> pokušati da "
"se poveže."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retry after"
msgstr "Pokušaj ponovo nakon:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the retrying interval here (in seconds)"
msgstr "Postavite period između pokušaja (u sekundama)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Interface"
msgstr "Veb sučelje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the web interface, check <guilabel>Enable Web Interface</"
"guilabel>; default port is 8080, and you configure any port higher than "
"1024. Then set <guilabel>User</guilabel> and <guilabel>Password</guilabel>. "
"You can access your web interface at http://127.0.0.1:&lt;port&gt;. You will "
"need to enter the username and password to get access."
msgstr ""
"Veb sučelje aktivirate popunjavanjem <guilabel>Upotreba veb sučelja</"
"guilabel>. Podrazumevani port je 8080, a možete zadati bilo koji iznad 1024. "
"Zatim popunite <guilabel>Korisnik:</guilabel> i <guilabel>Lozinka:</"
"guilabel>. Veb sučelju možete pristupiti na <literal>http://127.0.0.1:&lt;"
"port&gt;</literal>; unesite korisničko ime i lozinku da biste dobili pristup."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Web Interface</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo><application>KGetovo</application> veb sučelje.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Web Interface</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><application>KGetovo</application> veb sučelje.</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verification"
msgstr "Overa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verify your downloads."
msgstr "Overite preuzimanja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Verification</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Overa u <application>KGetu</application>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Verification</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Overa u <application>KGetu</application>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Using the two methods <guilabel>Automatic checksums verification</"
#| "guilabel> and <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> you can verify your "
#| "downloads. You just have to tick the Automatic verification check box."
msgid ""
"Using the two methods <guilabel>Automatic checksums verification</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> you can verify your downloads. You just "
"have to tick the <guilabel>Automatic verification</guilabel> check box."
msgstr ""
"Postoje dva metoda za overu preuzimanja, preko kontrolne sume ili potpisa. "
"Samo treba da popunite kućicu <guilabel>Automatska overa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration"
msgstr "Uklapanje"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use as download manager for Konqueror"
msgstr "Menadžer preuzimanja u K‑osvajaču"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set &kget; as your download manager for &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Postavite <application>KGet</application> za menadžer preuzimanja u "
"<application>K‑osvajaču</application>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monitor clipboard for files to download"
msgstr "Prati klipbord za fajlove za preuzimanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can turn on this feature that asks if you want to download &URL;s copied "
"into the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Možete da uključite mogućnost da budete pitani želite li da preuzmete URL "
"koji ste upravo kopirali u klipbord."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modify Advanced Options."
msgstr "Izmenite napredne opcije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Advanced Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Napredne opcije <application>KGeta</application>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Advanced Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredne opcije <application>KGeta</application>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable system tray icon"
msgstr "Uključi ikonicu u sistemskoj kaseti"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "This check box enables the &kget; system tray icon."
msgstr ""
"Popunjavanjem ove kućice aktivirate <application>KGetovu</application> "
"ikonicu sistemske kasete."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute action after all downloads have been finished"
msgstr "Radnja nakon što se sva preuzimanja završe:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to enable Quitting &kget; after all downloads have finished. "
"At startup you can choose to Restore Download state. Such as Stop All "
"downloads/ Start All downloads."
msgstr ""
"Popunite ovu kućicu da bi <application>KGet</application> bio napušten pošto "
"se završe sva preuzimanja. Pri pokretanju možete izabrati da obnovite stanje "
"preuzimanja, poput zaustavljanja ili pokretanja svih."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "History backend"
msgstr "Pozadina istorijata:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose your history backend as Sqlite or Xml."
msgstr "Izaberite da li će pozadina istorijata bili SQLite ili XML."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable &kde; global progress tracking"
msgstr "KDE‑ovo globalno praćenje napretka"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set &kget; to show every single download or show overall progress."
msgstr ""
"Možete zadati da <application>KGet</application> prikazuje svako preuzimanje "
"ponaosob, ili ukupan napredak."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Priključci"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
