msgstr "<phrase>Istorijat prenosa.</phrase>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a new window where you can see all the files downloaded using &kget;. "
"You can manage your history here, including filter and clear the history."
msgstr ""
"Otvara prozor u kojem možete videti sve fajlove preuzete "
"<application>KGetom</application>. Odavde možete upravljati istorijatom, "
"uključujući filtriranje i čišćenje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
